WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.300 --> 00:00:04.800
Child, why did you suddenly bring up this topic?

2
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:06.700
I was busy with work before

3
00:00:08.366 --> 00:00:10.233
After all this, I just realized

4
00:00:10.300 --> 00:00:12.166
You are the most important person to me

5
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.600
When this is all over

6
00:00:15.133 --> 00:00:17.366
We take our kids around the world.

7
00:00:19.166 --> 00:00:20.266
Okay?

8
00:00:21.366 --> 00:00:22.166
Wife

9
00:00:24.866 --> 00:00:26.266
President with information

10
00:00:27.866 --> 00:00:29.400
Go to your order that night

11
00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:31.033
To contain the native

12
00:00:33.966 --> 00:00:35.733
The photo must have fallen here.

13
00:00:35.733 --> 00:00:36.666
Why can't I find it?

14
00:00:36.666 --> 00:00:38.000
Are you looking for this?

15
00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.300
Unexpectedly, he ran into the range of Bicha Villa

16
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:43.800
That's the territory of the old lady Yin

17
00:00:44.066 --> 00:00:45.500
We dare not go in rashly

18
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.033
I can only let him run away

19
00:00:52.266 --> 00:00:55.033
It turned out that he was the one who kidnapped me that night

20
00:00:55.766 --> 00:00:58.500
Why would he go to grandma's place?

21
00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:03.466
The most ruthless person in my life is your Nangong family

22
00:01:04.666 --> 00:01:05.666
I remember.

23
00:01:05.666 --> 00:01:06.300
Yuan Sheng said

24
00:01:06.300 --> 00:01:08.300
He secretly hated everything about the Nangong family

25
00:01:08.700 --> 00:01:09.800
You think about it.

26
00:01:09.800 --> 00:01:11.633
Has your family offended anyone?

27
00:01:12.333 --> 00:01:13.133
Ah!

28
00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:14.933
When I was a kid

29
00:01:14.933 --> 00:01:17.200
My dad brought back an illegitimate child

30
00:01:17.566 --> 00:01:19.100
Kicked out by my mom

31
00:01:19.466 --> 00:01:22.633
That man, he seemed to say that I took everything from him

32
00:01:22.666 --> 00:01:23.600
To get revenge

33
00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.066
Now it looks like he had a big motive

34
00:01:27.533 --> 00:01:30.033
Maybe this person is native

35
00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:34.600
But the illegitimate child said he died in a car accident.

